            "title": "日股半日收漲2649點或4.96%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股今早大幅高開後持續在高位徘徊，日經平均指數半日漲2649點或4.96%，報56078點。</p>\n</div>",
