            "title": "滬指開市升40點 深成指升316點或2.36%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段跟隨外圍造好，上證綜指以3930點開市，升40點或1.03%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報13717點，更升316點或2.36%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升76點或1.73%，開報4517點；創業板指數開市報3257點，升97點或3.07%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15845904-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%8740%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87316%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%962-36",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 09:33:25",
